《夜航星》

执念的鱼
determined fish
提着灯跨过远洋的甄选
pulling lamp through the selection of faroceans 
继续下潜
diving on
无需誓言
with no oath
我的心像自沉的旧母舰
my heart is a drowning ship
没入深渊
sinking to the abyss
永别啊
farewell
我曾凝望
once I gazed
曾是航向的日出
at sunrise of my past destination
末路残烛
expiring candle
容我吹熄
let me blow it out
藏起火种
store the fire
向宇宙远渡
to the deep space sailing away 
点燃星
fire the star
亲手点燃目光尽头的准星
fire the target at the end of sight
让夜降临
bring the night fall
让陨石重启如萤火虫闪烁的飞行
fly the uranolith flickering  like a firefly
破灭魂灵
perish the soul
点燃星
fire the star
亲手点燃黑暗森林的火星
fire a fire star in the dark forest
蒙昧初醒
awakening
而我却轻声告别这新生的黎明
but I quietly bid farewell to the rising dawn


执念的鱼
determined fish
孤独着闯过远洋的甄选
pull through the selection of faroceans alone
文明岸边
by the shore of civilization
无需誓言
with no oath
我的心像重启的旧母舰
my heart is a restarted ship
去星云巅
to the peak of star cloud
永别啊
farewell
我曾凝望
once I gazed
曾是航向的日出
at the sunrise of my past destination
末路残烛
expiring candle
容我吹熄
let me blow it out
藏起火种
store the fire
向宇宙远渡
to the deep space sailing away
我是星
I am the star
利剑开刃寒光锋芒的银星
sharp and cold , the silver star
绝不消隐
no fading
不回顾永难再折返的故园的光阴
never look back to the times of past earth
决意前进
determined forward
我是星
I am the star
我愿投身前途未卜的群星
willing to throw to the unknown stars
为梦长明
shining for dream
让希望做我无声永存的墓志铭
make hope my silent epitaph
我是星
I am the star
利刃开锋寒光锋芒的银星
sharp and cold , the silver star
绝不消隐
no fading
不回顾永难再折返的故园的光阴
never look back to the times of past earth
决意前进
determined forward
点燃星
fire the star
亲手点燃黑暗森林的火星
fire a fire star in the dark forest
蒙昧初醒
awakening
而我却轻声告别这新生的黎明
yet I said farewell to the rising dawn